<li>May [deceased's name] rest in peace, and may your memories of them bring you peace.</li>
<li>Cherish the memories, and may they bring you solace.</li>
<li>May their soul find eternal rest and peace.</li>
<li>May peace find its way to your heart in this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>May you find peace in knowing that your loved one is at rest.</li>
<li>May the memories of [deceased's name] bring you strength and peace.</li>
<li>Remembering your loved one with warmth and peace.</li>
<li>May the love and light of your [relation] guide you through this time.</li>
<li>May you find comfort in the memories you shared.</li>
<li>Holding onto the beautiful memories you made together.</li>
<li>May you find peace in the love that surrounds you.</li>
<li>May your hearts find solace in the memories you hold dear.</li>
<li>May your sorrow ease with time, replaced by cherished memories.</li>
<li>May you find peace in the love you shared.</li>
    

      <h2 id="considerate-condolences-for-colleagues">Considerate Condolences for Colleagues</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>Keep the message professional yet empathetic, acknowledging the loss and offering support in a workplace context.</p>
<li>Please accept my deepest condolences on the loss of your [relation].</li>
<li>I am so sorry to hear of your loss.  Please let me know if there’s anything I can do to help with your workload.</li>
<li>My sincere condolences to you and your family. We're here to support you during this difficult time.</li>
<li>I was so saddened to hear about your loss. Please know that I'm thinking of you.</li>
<li>We offer our deepest sympathy and support to you during your time of sorrow.</li>
<li> Please accept my condolences.  We will be here for you should you need assistance with work.</li>
<li> We are deeply saddened by this news and send our heartfelt sympathy.</li>
<li>Our thoughts are with you and your family. Please let us know if there is anything we can do to support you.</li>
<li> Please accept our sincerest condolences.  We are here to help in any way possible.</li>
